==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Spiked
<hw>Spiked</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Furnished or set with
spikes, as corn; fastened with spikes; stopped with spikes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A youth, leaping over the <qex>spiked</qex> pales, . . . was
caught by those spikes.</q> <rj><qau>Wiseman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spikefish</ent>⟦br⟧
